00:27:36,447 --> 00:27:39,700
Good. This is Lieutenant McTaggert,
27th Precinct.

432
00:27:40,409 --> 00:27:41,994
<i>What can I do for you, Lieutenant?</i>

433
00:27:42,078 --> 00:27:45,206
