Thank you.

991
01:03:57,251 --> 01:03:58,544
(SPEAKS SPANISH)

992
01:03:59,503 --> 01:04:01,129
(PEOPLE SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY)

993
01:04:40,627 --> 01:04:42,254
What should we do?

994
