(EXCLAIMS)

995
01:05:11,158 --> 01:05:12,743
(SPEAKS IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE)

996
01:05:26,965 --> 01:05:29,051
Don't touch him! He's not one of us!

997
01:05:29,384 --> 01:05:30,385
Go! Quickly. Go now!

998
01:05:30,844 --> 01:05:32,095
(BOTH SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE)

999
